## The purpose of this script is to prepare a
## map showing the rate of tubewell ownership
## in each farm size category

## Farm size categories:
## 
## Marginal    : 0-1 Ha
## Small       : 1-2 Ha
## Semi-medium : 2-4 Ha
## Medium      : 4-6 Ha
## Large       : > 6 Ha

## Strategy is to downscale data from Minor
## Irrigation Census (1986-87)

## http://censusindia.gov.in/2011census/maps/administrative_maps/Final%20Atlas%20India%202011.pdf

